---
---

<section id="como-funciona" class="bg-bg-base py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2
        class="font-display mb-3 text-3xl font-bold text-text-strong md:text-4xl"
        style="font-family: var(--font-display); letter-spacing: -0.02em; text-wrap: balance;"
      >
        Tres pasos. Cero drama.
      </h2>
      <p class="font-body mx-auto text-lg text-text-muted" style="max-width: 44ch; text-wrap: pretty;">
        Desde escanear tu constancia hasta tener tu CFDI válido en menos de dos minutos.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 items-start gap-8 md:grid-cols-[1fr_auto_1fr_auto_1fr]">

      <div class="reveal stagger-1 flex flex-col items-center px-4 text-center">
        <h3 class="font-display mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-text-strong" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">
          Escanea tu constancia
        </h3>
        <div class="my-6 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-kipo-xl" style="background-color: var(--bg-subtle);">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--kipo-red)" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12.01" y2="18"/>
            <path d="M8 6h1M8 9h1M8 12h1"/>
            <path d="M12 6h4M12 9h4M12 12h4"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-base text-text-body" style="max-width: 28ch; text-wrap: pretty;">
          Sube tu Constancia de Situación Fiscal (el PDF del SAT con tu RFC y datos fiscales) y llenamos el resto solos.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-center justify-center py-2 text-text-muted md:py-0">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="rotate-90 transition-transform md:rotate-0" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal stagger-2 flex flex-col items-center px-4 text-center">
        <h3 class="font-display mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-text-strong" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">
          Crea tu factura
        </h3>
        <div class="my-6 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-kipo-xl" style="background-color: var(--bg-subtle);">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--kipo-red)" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/>
            <polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/>
            <polyline points="9 15 11 17 15 13"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-base text-text-body" style="max-width: 28ch; text-wrap: pretty;">
          Agrega el concepto, monto y datos de tu cliente. IVA calculado automáticamente según tu régimen.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-center justify-center py-2 text-text-muted md:py-0">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="rotate-90 transition-transform md:rotate-0" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal stagger-3 flex flex-col items-center px-4 text-center">
        <h3 class="font-display mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-text-strong" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">
          Timbra y cobra
        </h3>
        <div class="my-6 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-kipo-xl" style="background-color: var(--bg-subtle);">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--kipo-red)" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-base text-text-body" style="max-width: 28ch; text-wrap: pretty;">
          CFDI 4.0 válido ante el SAT en segundos. Envía por WhatsApp, correo o descarga el PDF.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
